  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a varied continental buffet with both hot and cold options including cereals, pastries, freshly made fruit tarts, fresh fruit, Tuscan and Italian cheeses and hot options such as sausages, scrambled eggs and bacon.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
